cc:Work.dc:title: Sonoj Convention Logo
cc:Work.dc:description: The logo of the Sonoj Convention. The font is a based on Sturkopf Grotesk by Uwe Borchert (SIL Open Font License) The white space left and right is two times the width of the small "o" from "convention" each. And top/bottom is the height of the same "o" each.
